---
title: Tikka Paneer Skewers with Cumin Seed Chips and Pickled Carrot Salad
description: Come rain or shine, it's time for a great British BBQ! Our summery dishes such as these Tikka Paneer Skewers are designed with full-on flavour in mind. Whether you enjoy it al fresco or bring some sunshine indoors, they're perfect for BBQ season.
